Telecom Italia Arm, Telefonica in Technology Accord, Cinco Says

-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 
2011-05-04T05:49:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-04/telecom-italia-arm-telefonica-in-technology-accord-cinco-says.html
Telefonica SA (TEF)  signed an agreement with
 Telecom Italia SpA (TIT) ’s voice messaging unit, Loquendo, to provide
technology for converting  text messages  into voice, Cinco Dias
reported, without saying where it got the information.  The agreement will enable the Spanish company to cut the
cost of services such as advertising distribution, the newspaper
said, adding that the technology will be used initially for
Telefonica’s business in  Spain .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
 eduarterubia@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
